  <summary date="2022-04-20T20:44:35Z" status="Introduced in House">Blockchain Solutions for Small Businesses Act

This bill requires the Small Business Administration to study the current and potential uses of blockchain technology (i.e., the technology that supports digital currencies such as Bitcoin) in making loans to qualified small businesses.</summary>
